---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Andrew Cordivari">
  <article class="about">
    <div class="about-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>This site.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        This is a space for writing about cloth, movement, and the things that hold attention over time.
      </p>

      <p>
        The fabrics section is the center of gravity — essays on the fibers, weaves, and constructions that define how clothing actually performs and ages. Merino wool, alpaca, technical synthetics like Gore-Tex and Schoeller, and the engineering of cotton from selvedge denim to Ventile.
      </p>

      <h2>Sections</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fabrics</strong> — Material essays on fiber, weave, and construction</li>
        <li><strong>Reflections</strong> — Longer thoughts on style and material culture</li>
        <li><strong>Learning</strong> — Notes from ongoing curiosity</li>
        <li><strong>Movement</strong> — A physical practice journal</li>
        <li><strong>Music</strong> — What's been on rotation</li>
        <li><strong>Birds</strong> — Field observations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>

      <p>
        <a href="mailto:andrew.cordivari@gmail.com">andrew.cordivari@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-header {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .prose {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .prose ul {
    padding-left: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .prose li {
    padding: 0.625rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .prose strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>
